*gruff-0.3.0 (13 Mar 2008)

  13 Mar 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -gruff-0.1.1.ebuild,
  -gruff-0.2.8.ebuild, +gruff-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Version bump: Fixed bug where pie graphs weren't drawing their label correctly.
  Remove old versions.

*gruff-0.2.9 (16 Nov 2007)

