  Version bump: Patch to make SideBar accurate instead of stacked.

  22 Jul 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> gruff-0.2.8.ebuild:
  Gruff does not work without truetype support in imagemagick: bug 186213.

  25 Mar 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> gruff-0.1.2.ebuild:
  ia64 stable wrt bug 155112

  04 Mar 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> gruff-0.2.8.ebuild:
  Add missing dependency on dev-ruby/hoe, #169306.

  24 Feb 2007; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> gruff-0.1.2.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 155112

